	]em
	" (友人マリオ 
	[em 
		"Yūjin Mario
	]em
	") is a Nicovideo phenomenon born from a person's desire to make his friend play his super-hard Mario hack and 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm3787152 rel=nofollow 
		"post the results on Nicovideo
	]a
	". By chance, this hack made its fame on Youtube when a team of Let's Play gamers obtained the hack and 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=83cID2roM6Q&list=UUCOQUAhIO8AJG2bQQ9F6BnQ&index=45 rel=nofollow 
		"recorded a video of them playing it
	]a
	". The most well-known YouTube video in this series is 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ua6pbz3ROvQ rel=nofollow 
		"the first part of ProtonJonSA's attempt of Special Stage 2 and his subsequent nervous breakdown
	]a
	".
	$LF
]p
[p 
