[p 
	"Themes that are common to Kaizo hacks:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Extremely rigid windows of opportunity, with missed opportunities resulting in death.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Set-ups that demand the highest caliber of Super Mario World physics abuse.
		$LF
